<H2>Design principles behind CSS2</H2>

<UL>
<LI>backward compatibility
<LI>complementary to structured documents
<LI>cascading
<LI>platform  &amp; device independence
<LI>accessibility
<LI>maintainability
<LI>network performance
</UL>

